sub_title: Innovative Program Manager in Education, Research, Labour Market, and International Development.
summary:
Dedicated and results-driven professional, with hands-on experience in project management, educational public policies, and youth employment. Proven success in coordinating teams, working in international settings, and fulfilling deadlines. I have built expertise in networking and coordinating. I am driven to make the world a better place. Believer in equality and justice, I have approached those topics throughout my studies and jobs, looking to contribute to settings where people lack the opportunities to live a life they value. Nowadays I wish to use what I have learned with a meaningful purpose. Having worked in different positions and environments, I can adapt, plan, organize, multitask, build relationships, lead teams, and deliver results on time and within budget. 

Interested in inequality, education, labor, and gender.
